--- Surf Theme ---

This map is meant to capture the essence and nostalgia of old surf maps that either felt classic to the surf community or stood out personally. I made unique surf for each theme while trying to mimic the style and personality of surf of each map. 

--- Description ---

Tier - 4 
Stages - 9
Bonuses - 3
